Package boundary

Class Summary
BoundaryCase Class for storing data coming from Boundary Case Library menu.
Constraint Class for constraint.
DispLoad Class for displacements (Inhomogeneous Dirichlet boundaries).
ElementMechLoad Class for element mechanical loads.
ElementTemp Class for element temperature loads.
InitialDisp Class for initial displacements (for dynamic analysis).
InitialVelo Class for initial velocities (for dynamic analysis).
NodalMechLoad Class for load (Neumann boundaries).
